      "content": "It sounds like you are experiencing profound grief over the loss of your professional identity, and that is incredibly painful. However, the foundation wasn't \"nothing\"; it was a complex body of work built on years of rigorous inquiry and dedication. Shifting your focus from past publications to future learning can allow you to re-evaluate your skills and passion. Even from this experience, you possess invaluable wisdom and resilience that can guide a completely new direction.",
